  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Reliability test of the FAST-O rating scale based on observational symptom ratings of patients with acute psychotic diseases</measure>
    <time_frame>Each patients symtoms will be rated on 2 occasions, by 2-3 raters, each. First is made within 24 hrs of admission to acute psychiatric care, secondis made 14 +/- 2 days after admittance, or earlier if the patient is discharged.</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
